{"tid":704450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【只是開端】標誌着中美數十年深化關係後，出現歷史變化；對華戰綫已隱隱成形","createTime":"2018-06-16T13:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T08:07:54.000Z","uid":147314,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f12de7b96a2fe89be4a370eae38d85d758083b1b","tid":704450,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2096553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2096553%2F&d=DsAE9f6syHjqdOw2cs4wHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3cc766c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2096553/</a><br />\n<br />\n貿易戰背後 中美掀科技競賽<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰火逼近，美國落實對中國進口商品加徵關稅、劍指中國高科技產品，一場由總統特朗普（Donald Trump）打響的技術競賽將會展開。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>分析憂慮 最終演變成新冷戰</strong><br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》形容特朗普的新貿易壁壘，標誌着中美數十年深化關係後，出現歷史變化。分析認為，這只是中美戰略博弈的開端，中美爭議長遠會超出經濟和科技領域，演變成全面對抗的新冷戰。<br />\n<br />\n回顧中美近期貿易談判，為減少美中巨額貿赤，中國聲言要擴大進口美國商品、給出明確數額，但仍打動不了特朗普。"},{"pid":"6d80b8f689a7b3b160c689e83c43c50c8b30e79c","tid":704450,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>美遏制華技術發展 非減貿赤</strong><br />\n<br />\n讓特朗普下定決心的，除了是美朝已開啟直接溝通管道、中國影響力下降外，美中貿易博弈亦關係到美國未來霸主地位，而美國已把中國定性為戰略競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述法國外貿銀行（Natixis）首席亞太區經濟學家埃雷羅（Alicia Garcia Herrero）亦稱，美國擬定的500億美元中國產品清單，旨在遏制中國的技術發展，而非減少雙邊貿赤，「我們已進入一場美國打響的技術競賽」。<br />\n<br />\n至於中美對抗如何發展，瑞穗證券亞洲公司首席經濟學家沈建光曾分析，短期貿易摩擦仍是主要分歧；中長期看，中國製造崛起及高技術領域與美國差距減少，中美或陷入零和困局，出現更多難以彌合的分歧。至於長期，中美問題超出經濟領域，出於「修昔底德陷阱（即新崛起大國必然要挑戰現存大國，而現存大國亦必然回應威脅，使戰爭不可避免）」的擔憂，美國對華全面反制非杞人憂天。<br />\n<br />\n除貿易制裁外，從美國印太政策、環太平洋軍演踢走中國，到美台關係升溫、通過《台灣旅行法》，美國對華全面對抗戰綫已隱隱成形。"},{"pid":"d702c9ee9c87d6f9571bbb4437178cb9b2bde531","tid":704450,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae20f804b8af0d177e6be76e73b42adf76a2b1e","tid":704450,"uid":104699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/australia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/south_korea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/france.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/germany.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346f50e8488723747839cdfa3df1823debf9392a","tid":704450,"uid":147314,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"bae20f804b8af0d177e6be76e73b42adf76a2b1e","tid":704450,"uid":104699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/australia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/south_korea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/france.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/germany.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pbs.twimg.com/media/BqF-F97IQAEodSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBqF-F97IQAEodSy.jpg&h=96bd1663&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8330bd90361b92bfdb69f60b207e49b902b2727a","tid":704450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f376f745bfd9e249aa89710a8909dcaff47491a","tid":704450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n2h<br />\n#China started trade war blocking U.S. companies,stealing their intellectual property &amp; forcing hand over of technology. Now they respond to ⁦new #TheftTax with tariffs that will raise price of food on their people. Lets see how that works out for them <br />\n<br />\nChina Issues Retaliatory Tariffs as Trade Fight Heats Up<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fwhite-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534&d=DsAE9f6syHjqdOw2cs4wHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=676f6f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534</a>"},{"pid":"69291322ae78a1e3e90f8e0cc099d72dcc710ff6","tid":704450,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f376f745bfd9e249aa89710a8909dcaff47491a","tid":704450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n2h<br />\n#China started trade war blocking U.S. companies,stealing their intellectual property &amp; forcing hand over of technology. Now they respond to ⁦new #TheftTax with tariffs that will raise price of food on their people. Lets see how that works out for them <br />\n<br />\nChina Issues Retaliatory Tariffs as Trade Fight Heats Up<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fwhite-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534&d=DsAE9f6syHjqdOw2cs4wHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=676f6f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"平價豬糧沒了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a258905d20ed0ddf07d831c2731cdd851